For scripts etc (sdaN changes)

/dev/disk/by-id/NNN         ID from bussystem, device-name, model
                            or serial number
/dev/disk/by-label/label    name from filesystem
/dev/disk/by-path/xxx       name by PCI-Interface, bus-system and
                            partition number
                            USB-Sticks on other Ports have different number!
/dev/disk/by-uuid/nnn       UUID